<title>How to get help</title>

<p>To receive help on problems you can send an email to the <link href="http://mail.gnome.org/mailman/listinfo/evolution-list">Evolution mailing list</link> or talk to developers and other users in the IRC chat channel #evolution on the server irc.gimp.net. To connect to an IRC server you can for example use the internet messenger application Empathy.</p>

